{"article_id":"wLCoUuAqlc4B7AHM","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As far back as last October ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"when the special counsel Robert Mueller indicted Paul Manafort and his protégé , Rick Gates , on charges of conspiracy","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to launder money","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and failure to disclose foreign bank accounts ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"it was clear that the two men were in serious trouble .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Court documents accused Manafort and Gates of generating \" tens of millions of dollars in income \" in the past decade and a half","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"while working for entities","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"associated with Viktor Yanukovych , the pro-Russia former President of Ukraine ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and laundering the money \" through scores of United States and foreign corporations , partnerships and bank accounts . \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Earlier this year , Gates ,","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"who is forty-six ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"reached a plea deal with Mueller ' s team ,","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"in which he pleaded guilty to a number of charges","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and agreed to coöperate with the investigation against his former boss .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"On Monday , he began his testimony in a courtroom in Alexandria , Virginia ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"where Manafort ' s first trial is taking place .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"( There is a second trial scheduled in Washington , D.C . )","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"This was the fifth day of the trial .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Given the bitter controversy","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"surrounding the scope of Mueller ' s investigation into Russia ' s attempts","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"to disrupt the 2016 Presidential election ,","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Manafort ' s trial has inevitably sparked a great deal of speculation","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"about how it fits in ,","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"or doesn ' t fit in , to the broader picture .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"Manafort served as Donald Trump ' s campaign manager for three months in 2016 .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"During that time , Manafort , among other things , attended the now notorious Trump Tower meeting with a group of Russians","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"who","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"the Trump campaign believed","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"had dirt on Hillary Clinton .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Gates served as Trump ' s deputy campaign manager under Manafort","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"and also worked for Trump ' s transition team , the group","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that worked to staff and prepare Trump ' s incoming Administration in the weeks after Election Day .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"But so far , in Manafort ' s trial , the focus has remained firmly on events","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"that took place well in advance of Trump ' s bid for the Presidency .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"On Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"before calling Gates to the witness stand ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"the prosecutors finished up extracting information from one of Manafort ' s tax accountants , Cindy Laporta , from the firm Kositzka , Wicks & Company ,","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"who had already testified","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"that , in 2015 ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"relying on instructions from Gates and Manafort ,","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"she falsified tax documents","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"to save Manafort money","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and help him obtain bank loans .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Then an expert on financial crimes at the Treasury Department , Paula Liss , explained to the jury","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"that it is a crime to set up bank accounts overseas","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"and not report them to the I.R.S . or other government agencies .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Between 2011 and 2014 ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Liss said ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"neither Manafort nor his wife reported having any such accounts .","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"A short time later ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Gates stepped into the witness box .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"The reports from inside the courtroom all say","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"that Gates avoided looking at Manafort ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"who was staring at him from the defense table","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"with his arms folded .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Instead , Gates kept his gaze fixed on the government ' s lead prosecutor , Greg Andres ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"who made his bones","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"prosecuting mobsters in the U.S. Attorney ' s Office for the Eastern District of New York .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"After briefly guiding Gates through how he came to meet Manafort","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"and work for him ,","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Andres asked ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"\" Were you involved in any criminal activity with Mr. Manafort ? \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Gates replied ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"\" Yes. \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Andres then asked ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"\" Did you commit any crimes with Mr. Manafort ? \"","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"Gates said ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"\" Yes . \"","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Andres pressed for details .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Gates said","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"that he conspired to falsify Manafort ' s tax returns","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"by lying to his accountants about his finances .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"that he had done that \" at Mr. Manafort ' s request. \"","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"He also said","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"that he and Manafort had set up fifteen foreign bank accounts","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"without disclosing them to the U.S. government ,","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"and that they failed to register Manafort as a foreign agent .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"\" When asked why he had lied ,","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"Gates said","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"he had done so at Manafort ' s request , \" the Washington Post ' s excellent live blog reported . \"","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"Separately , Gates explained","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that Manafort had directed him to report money","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"wired from his foreign bank accounts as loans , rather than as income ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"to reduce Manafort ' s taxable income .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"By reporting it as a loan ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Gates explained ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Manafort could defer the amount of taxes","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"he owed . \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Before the day ended ,","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"Gates began answering more detailed questions about the work","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"he and Manafort did in Ukraine ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"starting in 2007 .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"He explained","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"how the payments to Manafort ' s firm were wired to shell companies in Cyprus , a Mediterranean island","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"known for its lax banking laws and popularity with wealthy Russians .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Once the money was there ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Gates said ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Manafort would move some of it to his U.S. accounts .","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"Gates ' s testimony ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"which will continue on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"strengthened the impression","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"that Manafort ' s lawyers will need to present a strong defense","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"to save him .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"( That ' s if Trump doesn ' t issue him a Presidential pardon . )","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"They have already signalled their strategy :","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"blame everything on Gates ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"and argue","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"that he is now lying","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"to save his own skin .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"During his cross-examination of Laporta , Kevin Downing , Manafort ' s lead attorney , sought to emphasize","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"how much the accountant relied on information","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"provided by Gates rather than Manafort ,","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"and he made a bit of headway there .","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"But the defense team ' s best moment of the day came","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"when Gates was on the stand","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"answering questions from the prosecution .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"Gates testified","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"in addition to committing the crimes","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"he copped to in his plea agreement ,","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"he embezzled money from Manafort ' s consulting firm .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"\" I added money to expense reports","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"and created expense reports , \"","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"estimating","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that the sums","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"involved came to \" several hundred thousand \" dollars .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"Gates said","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"that he also stole money from other people at Manafort ' s firm ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"told lies to Mueller ' s investigators initially ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"and lied in a civil case against Manafort .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"As part of his agreement with the government ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"he added ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"the prosecutors had agreed not to bring charges on these matters .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"It is customary for coöperating witnesses , at the start of their testimony , to make a clean breast of things ,","depth":6},{"id":136,"text":"so they can not get caught out on subsequent questioning by the defense .","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"Still , Gates ' s admissions will give Downing something","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"to go on","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"when he begins his cross-examination .","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"Almost certainly , that will be the most dramatic bit of the trial .","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"Whether it will affect the outcome remains to be seen .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":175,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":159,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":150,"right":158,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":145,"right":4,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":0,"right":144,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":143,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":5,"right":148,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":147,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":151,"right":153,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":151,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":11,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":157,"left":156,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":1